{"tid":1695134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」英國內政部：預計將撤銷林鄭月娥全家英國國籍","createTime":"2019-11-05T12:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T21:54:36.000Z","uid":18024,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"13a490513713bed36a0b24905e83ac6616284a79","tid":1695134,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/breakup1984/status/1191288489234464769?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbreakup1984%2Fstatus%2F1191288489234464769%3Fs%3D21&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=acc27d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbreakup1984%2Fstatus%2F1191288489234464769%3Fs%3D21&h=de66fdc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/breakup1984/status/1191288489234464769?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n英國內政部：預計將撤銷林鄭月娥全家英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n消息人士引英國內政部不願透露姓名官員，預計英國政府將在三周內正式回應，如無意外情況會撤銷林鄭月娥全家英國國籍。<br />\n<br />\n該官員強調，英國幾個世紀以來都在堅守英國價值與通行的文明規則。英國不會因爲雙向對等商業利益而放棄自己文明底綫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIhOVljXsAEtr9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEIhOVljXsAEtr9n.jpg&h=e670c7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af06da2bde42f4a53fd7a89817566f265654e6e","tid":1695134,"uid":33028,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"fake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ed53880cf6b03054a83c42c0d871aeb82c4921","tid":1695134,"uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"無reliable source ..."},{"pid":"9b95e4a03011b63bc7357064a59bfea37d5c755e","tid":1695134,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,